```plantuml
@startuml Neighbor-Army_help-with-covid

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Firebase Auth" as Auth
participant "Firebase Functions" as Backend
participant "Onfleet API" as Onfleet
participant "Sendgrid API" as Sendgrid
participant "Twilio API" as Twilio
participant "Google Maps API" as Maps

User -> Frontend: Accesses application
Frontend -> Auth: Authenticates user
Auth --> Frontend: Returns auth token

alt Request Help
    User -> Frontend: Submits help request
    Frontend -> Maps: Validates address
    Maps --> Frontend: Returns validated address
    Frontend -> Backend: Sends help request
    Backend -> Onfleet: Creates task
    Onfleet --> Backend: Confirms task creation
    Backend --> Frontend: Returns confirmation
    Frontend --> User: Shows success message

else Offer Help
    User -> Frontend: Submits volunteer form
    Frontend -> Twilio: Verifies phone/zipcode
    Twilio --> Frontend: Returns verification result
    Frontend -> Backend: Registers volunteer
    Backend -> Onfleet: Creates worker
    Onfleet --> Backend: Confirms worker creation
    Backend -> Sendgrid: Adds to mailing list
    Sendgrid --> Backend: Confirms subscription
    Backend --> Frontend: Returns confirmation
    Frontend --> User: Shows success message
end

@enduml
```